title: Dan Patrick -  Hour 3 - Nike Bribe & Greg Olsen Talks Baker
itunes:title: Dan Patrick -  Hour 3 - Nike Bribe & Greg Olsen Talks Baker
description:
Rich Davis and Ryan Hollins are having a lot of fun filling-in for Dan Patrick, as they begin hour 3 by talking lemonade stands, "gal garage" and buying off jersey numbers. The Mets Jeff McNeil received a top tier Rolex from Starling Marte in order to get his #4...what did Ryan receive from a teammate? A caller celebrates Snoop Dogg Day and the legendary TE/now broadcaster Greg Olsen calls the show to talk NFL!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
